Package it.polimi.ingsw.server.controller

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BuilderBuildObserver
    This interface is implemented to be informed about a new build from src to dst, of a dome or not.
    BuilderMoveObserver
    This interface is implemented to be informed about a new move from src to dst.
    BuilderSetupObserver
    This interface is implemented to be informed about a new builders placement.
    ColorChoiceObserver
    This interface is implemented to be informed about a new builders color choice by a player.
    ConnectionObserver
    This interface is implemented to be informed about a new connection, disconnection or earlyDisconnection.
    GodCardChoiceObserver
    This interface is implemented to be informed about a choice of single player godCard or match godCards.
    NewPlayerObserver
    This interface is implemented to be informed about a new player insertion.
    NumberOfPlayersObserver
    This interface is implemented to be informed about number of players insertion.
    StartPlayerObserver
    This interface is implemented to be informed of start player set.
    StepChoiceObserver
    This interface is implemented to be informed about a step choice.
